"title": "6677: justification, necessity of",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "6677: justification, necessity of",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>Sinful, law-breaking humanity needs a means of justification because of its failure to keep God's law and live up to God's requirements.</p>\n<h2>Justification in human relationships</h2>\n<h3>The acquittal of the innocent</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut25:1\">DEU 25:1</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Prov17:15\">PRO 17:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:9\">ISA 43:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa43:26\">ISA 43:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:33\">ROM 8:33</a></p>\n<h3>Justification of oneself</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job32:2\">JOB 32:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:29\">LUK 10:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:15\">LUK 16:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a></p>\n<h2>The need for justification</h2>\n<h3>The reality of God's righteousness</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps11:7\">PSA 11:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:5\">PSA 33:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps35:28\">PSA 35:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:6\">JER 23:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt6:33\">MAT 6:33</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John17:25\">JHN 17:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:17\">ROM 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:22\">ROM 3:22</a></p>\n<h3>The reality of God's justice</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps9:8\">PSA 9:8</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job36:3\">JOB 36:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps11:7\">PSA 11:7</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps33:5\">PSA 33:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa5:16\">ISA 5:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer9:24\">JER 9:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:7\">LUK 18:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev19:11\">REV 19:11</a></p>\n<h3>The reality of God's judgment</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen18:25\">GEN 18:25</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Judg11:27\">JDG 11:27</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps51:4\">PSA 51:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Mic6:2\">MIC 6:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt12:36\">MAT 12:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom2:16\">ROM 2:16</a></p>\n<h3>The reality of God's law</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jas4:12\">JAS 4:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod20:2-Exod20:17\">EXO 20:2–20:17</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:6-Deut5:21\">DEU 5:6–5:21</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps19:7\">PSA 19:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa33:22\">ISA 33:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:12\">ROM 7:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom7:16\">ROM 7:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:3-Rom8:4\">ROM 8:3–8:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim1:8\">1TI 1:8</a></p>\n<h2>Human guilt shows the need for justification</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps143:2\">PSA 143:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:23\">ROM 3:23</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:8\">1JN 1:8</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1John1:10\">1JN 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>People are unable to justify themselves, even through the law</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa64:6\">ISA 64:6</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:20-Rom3:21\">ROM 3:20–3:21</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:15-Gal2:16\">GAL 2:15–2:16</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Amos4:4\">AMO 4:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:20\">MAT 5:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke10:29\">LUK 10:29</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke16:15\">LUK 16:15</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke18:9-Luke18:14\">LUK 18:9–18:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom1:17\">ROM 1:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom3:20\">ROM 3:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:21\">GAL 2:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal3:2-Gal3:3\">GAL 3:2–3:3</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal2:11\">GAL 2:11</a> <em>Paul opposes Peter's position on circumcision</em>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gal5:4\">GAL 5:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil3:4-Phil3:8\">PHP 3:4–3:8</a></p>",
